<doc id="1277285" wikidata="Q16874472" url="?curid=1277285" title="Monark 540">
<text>The Monark 540 is a sailboat. It has four beds and a small kitchen under one of the beds.

==History==
The Monark 540 was designed by Pelle Petterson for Monark in 1972.

